    a href="https://github.com/nathanaeljones/weaver-lua" Lua implementation
    a href="http://weaverengine.com" Home page

    h5 SuperCopy
    a href="http://supercopy.codeplex.com" SuperCopy lets you simulate copies, merges, and makes XCopy easy to use (2005)
    h5 QuickKey
    a href="/quickkey" QuickKey is a Character Map alternative I wrote in 2001, which became very popular with multi-lingual users.

